text: Bilochwala is a town located in the Punjab province of Pakistan. It is located in Faisalabad District at 31°17'0N 73°4'0E with an altitude of 171 metres (567 feet) and lies near to the city of Lahore.Location of Bilochwala - Falling Rain Genomics Neighbouring settlements include Bismillapur to the west and Miranpur, Punjab to the east. ==References== Category:Populated places in Faisalabad District
title: Bilochwala
